items.title: Cloud Data Fusion launched on GCP
items.description: Cloud Data Fusion is a fully managed, cloud-native, enterprise data integration service, powered by CDAP, for quickly building and managing data pipelines on Google Cloud Platform. Visit the Google Cloud Console to try it out today.
